47
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:11,960
He must be punished by the law of Tang.

48
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:34,320
After you go back to Magistrate's Office,

49
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,200
tell Mr. Hong

50
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:39,080
to withdraw 2,000 qian

51
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:43,000
and send it to Zhou Changyi's family

52
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:44,480
in Zhou Village, Mei County,

53
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:46,800
Ezhou.

54
00:05:57,080 --> 00:05:57,880
I'll leave

55
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,360
this place to you.

56
