found no trace of Han Yongnan.

123
00:12:07,880 --> 00:12:08,800
Is it possible

124
00:12:08,800 --> 00:12:09,640
that he has gone to his brother

125
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:10,920
in Liangzhou?

126
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:14,080
Magistrate,

127
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:16,440
