165
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:49,160
and a veil?

166
00:14:51,040 --> 00:14:51,960
Which way did you see

167
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:53,320
them going?

168
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:16,600
My surname is Diao.

169
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:18,040
My given name is Xiaoguan.

170
00:15:19,280 --> 00:15:20,200
Let's have a chat.

171
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:22,840
An hour ago,

172
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:24,880
he was heading for Yiwu County.

173
00:15:25,040 --> 00:15:26,440
Even if we ride as fast as we can,

174
00:15:26,840 --> 00:15:28,080
it will take us a day
to catch up with him.

175
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:29,200
Magistrate,

176
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:31,160
he has been following us all along.

177
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:33,160
This is the frontier Zhenxi Fortress.

178
00:15:33,680 --> 00:15:34,680
It's the westmost place.

179
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:35,880
Follow me.

180
00:15:36,160 --> 00:15:37,240
I might have seen the man

181
00:15:37,760 --> 00:15:38,280
you are looking for.

182
00:15:38,280 --> 00:15:40,440
I don't understand your law or rules,

183
00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:41,480
nor do I want to understand them.

184
00:15:41,560 --> 00:15:42,760
But I know

185
00:15:44,040 --> 00:15:45,440
all men, no matter how high or low,

186
00:15:45,680 --> 00:15:46,920
are beasts

187
00:15:47,360 --> 00:15:48,320
beneath the skin.

188
00:15:49,360 --> 00:15:51,200
It's just that some are domineering

189
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:52,960
and some are trampled upon.

190
00:15:53,400 --> 00:15:55,560
Han Yongnan is a dhole in Lanfang County,

191
00:15:55,560 --> 00:15:56,880
showing his teeth.

192
00:15:58,040 --> 00:15:59,040
But in this place,

193
00:15:59,760 --> 00:16:01,320
he is not even a rat.

194
00:16:01,880 --> 00:16:03,520
He could be torn into pieces at any time.

195
00:16:04,160 --> 00:16:05,560
It turns out

196
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:07,520
you have never left.

197
00:16:11,400 --> 00:16:12,000
Han Yongnan,

198
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:13,120
it serves you right.

199
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:21,400
Well done.

200
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:23,480
Think about your sister.

201
00:16:25,560 --> 00:16:27,000
Think about what he has done.

202
00:16:34,400 --> 00:16:35,600
The knife is in your hand.

203
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:37,520
You can let him

204
00:16:37,520 --> 00:16:38,680
feel your pain.

205
00:16:44,920 --> 00:16:45,440
Don't be afraid.

206
00:16:46,640 --> 00:16:48,640
This is the punishment he deserves.

207
00:16:50,560 --> 00:16:51,120
Wangdong,

208
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:53,280
kill him.

209
00:16:57,800 --> 00:16:58,680
Kill him!

210
00:16:59,600 --> 00:17:00,280
Wangdong,

211
00:17:01,040 --> 00:17:01,880
