Kill him!

213
00:17:09,760 --> 00:17:10,560
Stop!

214
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:17,120
Magistrate, save me!

215
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:22,720
You came faster than I thought.

216
00:17:23,600 --> 00:17:25,080
He's been in Lanfang County.

217
00:17:25,480 --> 00:17:27,120
He has never left.

218
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:28,840
Everything

219
00:17:28,840 --> 00:17:30,080
has been arranged by you.

220
00:17:30,680 --> 00:17:32,080
How could it be possible, Daguan?

221
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:33,960
I just found you

222
00:17:34,360 --> 00:17:35,560
interesting

223
00:17:36,040 --> 00:17:37,360
and was going along for the ride.

224
00:17:38,520 --> 00:17:39,360
Magistrate Di,

225
00:17:40,240 --> 00:17:41,080
do you know?

226
00:17:41,840 --> 00:17:43,720
Han Yongnan has already dug

227
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:45,040
this place into an illegal mining hole.

228
00:17:45,600 --> 00:17:47,200
If you dig three chi down,

229
00:17:47,240 --> 00:17:48,080
you can dig through the ground.

230
00:17:53,960 --> 00:17:55,000
You don't know it.

231
00:17:56,040 --> 00:17:56,560
Look,

232
00:17:57,960 --> 00:17:59,040
as a magistrate,

233
00:17:59,920 --> 00:18:01,360
you don't even know this.

234
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:04,160
Wangdong,

235
00:18:04,880 --> 00:18:05,920
put the knife down.

236
00:18:07,080 --> 00:18:08,560
I will punish him for his crime.

237
00:18:08,560 --> 00:18:09,360
Punish him?

238
00:18:10,640 --> 00:18:11,600
Based on what?

239
00:18:11,760 --> 00:18:12,560
Do you have evidence?

240
00:18:13,840 --> 00:18:14,920
He didn't kill anyone.

241
00:18:15,600 --> 00:18:17,520
I killed those two singsong girls.

242
00:18:20,880 --> 00:18:21,680
Wangdong,

243
00:18:22,280 --> 00:18:23,320
put the knife down.

244
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:25,920
I have found him now.

245
00:18:26,520 --> 00:18:28,920
I'll give him the punishment he deserves.

246
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:30,800
You can't kill him.

247
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:32,040
Think about it, Wangdong.

248
00:18:32,040 --> 00:18:33,480
How did he release Han Yongnan?

249
00:18:33,720 --> 00:18:35,360
Do you trust him or yourself?

250
00:18:35,360 --> 00:18:36,720
If you kill him,
you will also commit a crime.

251
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:38,440
You can take revenge with a knife in hand.

252
00:18:40,120 --> 00:18:40,840
Go to hell!

253
00:18:41,080 --> 00:18:41,800
Wangdong!

254
00:18:48,040 --> 00:18:48,560
Wangdong,

255
00:18:49,080 --> 00:18:50,200
put the knife down.

256
00:18:50,600 --> 00:18:52,800
Han Yongnan will get the punishment
he deserves.

257
00:18:53,110 --> 00:18:54,320
Don't be silly.

258
00:18:55,320 --> 00:18:57,000
Have you always been this stubborn?

259
00:18:58,080 --> 00:18:59,240
I thought

260
