270
00:19:20,960 --> 00:19:21,800
He is a good man.

271
00:19:22,120 --> 00:19:22,880
He helped me.

272
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:24,760
Did you hear that?

273
00:19:25,520 --> 00:19:27,880
He needs me. He needs us.

274
00:19:28,520 --> 00:19:30,640
If the government is so indiscriminate,

275
00:19:31,240 --> 00:19:32,280
it's worse than Heiyan.

276
00:19:32,760 --> 00:19:33,920
As long as we joined them,

277
00:19:34,280 --> 00:19:35,360
they would help us get rid of the people

278
00:19:35,360 --> 00:19:36,560
who hurt us.

279
00:19:36,800 --> 00:19:37,840
They are talking nonsense.

280
00:19:37,840 --> 00:19:38,960
Who told you this?

281
00:19:39,360 --> 00:19:40,600
Heiyan is better than you.

282
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:44,320
Don't listen to him.

283
00:19:44,720 --> 00:19:46,320
He is from Heiyan.

284
00:19:47,120 --> 00:19:48,440
At least, we can give him

285
00:19:48,440 --> 00:19:50,320
justice that you can't give.

286
00:19:54,840 --> 00:19:55,680
Wangdong,

287
00:19:56,160 --> 00:19:56,960
do it now.

288
00:19:57,320 --> 00:19:58,560
